  <h2 class="casual">Casual</h2>
  <p>The easiest dress code to follow, casual dress one might say is the lack of a dress code. Sneakers, jeans, onesies, they're all acceptable at a casual establishment. Cities in California and cities like Berlin are famous for their trendy casual wear.</p><br>
  <p>"Anything goes in this case, including jeans and sneakers, and this dress code usually means you’ll be uncomfortable in anything too dressy."</p>
  <hr>
